
Objective:-  To build a web page in Angular JS to change template theme and image resize.

Details:-

1.       A webpage should be built and displayed With some welcome text and image.

2.       There should be 3 input boxes to take font type, font color and background color.

3.       User should be able to choose font type, font color and background color from those text boxes.

4.       There should be a submit  button to take the above inputs.

5.       Once, submitted, the font type of welcome text, font color and background color of web page should change.

6.       Font color and webpage bg color should not be same, appropriate message to be displayed to user as pop up.

7.       The page should be compatible for mobile view.

8.       There should be an input to display the number of images. Images should get displayed in grid layout  4 in a row for desktop site and 2 in a row for mobile site.

9.       Same image can be re-used as per the count selected.

Technologies to Use

1.       Angular JS version 4

2.       HTML5

3.       CSS

4.       JS

5.       Bootstrap